astes how you might expect it.\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1523, \"end\": 1528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoji\", \"score\": 0.9035654510198982, \"rank\": 0.10672668612039547, \"text\": \"Shoji\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoji\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoji\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"similar thoughts\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"the grilled chicken\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not terrible, not great.\\\"\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete concluded his video by eating the last thing on his plate, grilled tofu, which he could \\\"barely cut.\\\"\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athlete\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"his video\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"the last thing\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"his plate\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"grilled tofu\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not great but it's OK,\\\" he said about the tofu.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tofu\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's OK guys.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"OK guys\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's super late at night.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only one section of the dining hall was open.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only one section\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"the dining hall\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So far, the food's been good.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's 12:30 at night, I am going to finish this meal and go to bed.\\\"\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"this meal\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In anotherTikTok video, Olympic gymnast Aleah Finnegan, who's competing for the Philippines, documented her experience at the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2050, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aleah Finnegan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\"}, {\"begin\": 2090, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999998506609811, \"rank\": 1.3106271173926306e-07, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anotherTikTok video\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"her experience\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After filming her walk through the food hall, she then sat down with her tray and gave her mixed thoughts about the food.\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the food hall\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"her tray\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"her mixed thoughts\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, the food is good.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not really seasoned,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a seasoning station over there.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a seasoning station\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not bad, it's just pretty basic\\u2026 It's pretty good, it's good food.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good food\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It just probably needs some seasoning a little bit.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some seasoning\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Personal preference, that's me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Raven Saunders - a Team USA track and field star - is not a fan of the food at all.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2551, \"end\": 2565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raven_Saunders\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Raven Saunders\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raven_Saunders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raven_Saunders\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Team USA track and field star\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"a fan\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the text overher TikTok videoread: \\\"Eating in the Olympics like\\u2026\\\" she held up what appeared to be a burnt piece of meat on a stick.\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2655, \"end\": 2661, \"title\":